extendedInfo.description: Drag Racing Best Tunes Lite. This is the FREE version of the best Drag Racing tunes app on the market. It has the first, second and third level pro tunes unlocked. The full version is available here: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.dingerapps.drtunes The app contains tunes for cars in the Drag Racing app by Creative Mobile. These tunes and Drag Racing setups will make you win in all your pro league races and even set you up to break records. Drag Racing Best Tunes Lite also provides you with guides to help you gain better times with your cars. Try it out, it's FREE isn't it.QUARTER MILE TUNESLevel 1 - BMW 328is E38 (12.328)Level 2 - Mazda RX-8 (10.591)Level 3 - Pontiac GTO (9.972)Level 4 - BMW M3 E92 (9.934)Level 5 - Dodge Charger SRT8 (9.247)Level 6 - Lamborghini Gallardo LP 570 (8.763)Level 7 - Ford RS200 (8.277)Level 8 - Lamborghini Murcielago LP 670 (7.96)Level 9 - SSC Ultimate Aero (7.759)Level 10 - SSC Tuatara (7.462)HALF MILE TUNESLevel 1 - Renault Clio V6 Sport (19.625)Level 2 - Mazda RX-8 (17.084)Level 3 - Pontiac GTO (15.988)Level 4 - Honda NSX-R (14.869)Level 5 - BMW M5 E60 (14.27)Level 6 - Mercades Brabus SLS 700 (13.576)Level 7 - Koenigsegg Agera R (12.731)Level 8 - Koenigsegg Agera R (11.934)Level 9 - SSC Ultimate Aero (11.643)Level 10 - SSC Tuatara (11.044)BONUS TUNESBMW M5 (9.285)
